{"tid":1224903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰你隻爛袋狗","createTime":"2019-06-15T05:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T07:31:11.000Z","uid":25163,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"37d6c2b206177ae9b40cdd2456a3ac42887bad61","tid":1224903,"uid":25163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"你以為你仲可以平安無事咁坐係一哥個位咩?<br />\n依家全世界人都睇撚住警犬胡亂使用武力 亂開槍 射記者 10個圍一個手無寸鐵既市民<br />\n反送中成功與否 落幕第一件事就係問你條仆街責 容許下屬係毫無準則情況下使用武力<br />\n一哥 仲有得坐個陣好坐穩啲 依家共產黨都唔攬條柒婆<br />\n好撚快你就係下一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a85237118584bd0d1cbd9bf87605095f642db4a","tid":1224903,"uid":207087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"支持喇叭中學清理門戶"},{"pid":"477c9eafcf6a52c8a0bf75abbd09ab673c103689","tid":1224903,"uid":25163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0a85237118584bd0d1cbd9bf87605095f642db4a","tid":1224903,"uid":207087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"支持喇叭中學清理門戶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:46:29.000Z","msg":"輕鬆成為人民公敵 連自己母校師弟都表示喇沙之恥 <br />\n一哥係時候寫定稿諗下點樣引咎辭職啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef15186a267781df7ab1657daae6d4b1ae6ea5a9","tid":1224903,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:58:32.000Z","msg":"2018年果陣寫佢延長任期一年, 即係2019年11月就退<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處處長盧偉聰及副處長（行動）劉業成將於今年11月屆57歲退休年齡，為方便警隊管理層順利交接，政府昨公佈，原於今年11月19日屆退休年齡的盧偉聰獲延任一年至明年11月18日。據悉，劉業成會按照原定計劃退休，預料現任行動處處長鄧炳強會接替劉業成擢升副處長，鄧更成為下任警隊「一哥」的熱門人選。<br />\n記者：謝明明 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180914/20499188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20499188&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=6f9978ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20499188&h=907fcd88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180914/20499188</a>"},{"pid":"6243f4c6ce877379b599eaae9eb61192bf0feb99","tid":1224903,"uid":25163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef15186a267781df7ab1657daae6d4b1ae6ea5a9","tid":1224903,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:58:32.000Z","msg":"2018年果陣寫佢延長任期一年, 即係2019年11月就退<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處處長盧偉聰及副處長（行動）劉業成將於今年11月屆57歲退休年齡，為方便警隊管理層順利交接，政府昨公佈，原於今年11月19日屆退休年齡的盧偉聰獲延任一年至明年11月18日。據悉，劉業成會按照原定計劃退休，預料現任行動處處長鄧炳強會接替劉業成擢升副處長，鄧更成為下任警隊「一哥」的熱門人選。<br />\n記者：謝明明 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180914/20499188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20499188&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=6f9978ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20499188&h=907fcd88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180914/20499188</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"已經想像到呢幾個月會有幾多人圍剿佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43478427c39781f67b4fd61e904f4f5220311c3","tid":1224903,"uid":25163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:31:11.000Z","msg":"要求柒婆撤回修例<br />\n下一步就係各界人士立刻問責警務處處長盧偉聰<br />\n成立透明小組調查警隊過去一星期既不當執法 <br />\n嚴懲沒有跟隨指示的警員以為胡亂下令的警官 <br />\n並且釋放所有被無理拘捕既遊行人士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}